The paper proposes a novel deep learning model for predicting taxi demand between all region pairs, which involves the modeling of local spatial context, temporal evolution context, and global correlation context. This task and approach are closely related to several sub-fields in computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
